OL,3,CMan denies trying to kill fellow
OL,4,Cteacher with knife after rejection
OL,6,FA teacher has denied attempting to
OL,7,Fmurder his on-off partner with a knife
OL,8,Fafter failing to accept that their
OL,9,Frelationship was over.
OL,11,FMatthew Jones, 28, admits causing
OL,12,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent to
OL,13,FEmma Kirk, 24, after they met in a
OL,14,Flane in Bath, Somerset, in February.
OL,16,FBristol Crown Court has heard Jones
OL,17,Fstabbed Miss Kirk, a fellow teacher,
OL,18,Fabout 15 times with the blade `
OL,19,Finflicting injuries to her neck, head
OL,20,Fand face.
