OL,3,CMan denies trying to kill fellow
OL,4,Cteacher with knife after rejection
OL,6,FJurors have been told that the attack
OL,7,Fwas so frenzied that it took five men
OL,8,Fto drag Jones off Miss Kirk, and even
OL,9,Fthen he tried to strangle her.
OL,11,FBut giving evidence in his trial,
OL,12,FJones insisted he was not intending to
OL,13,Fkill Miss Kirk during the incident and
OL,14,Fclaimed she had brought the knife to
OL,15,Fthe scene, not him.
OL,17,FDuring cross-examination, Jones said
OL,18,Fhe accepted stabbing Miss Kirk once
OL,19,Fbut claimed the other injuries she
OL,20,Fsustained were "cuts".
