OL,6,FHe told the jury: "If I had wanted to
OL,7,Fkill Emma at any point, Emma would not
OL,8,Fbe here now.
OL,10,FJones added: "I could have caused
OL,11,Fmaximum damage by stabbing her in as
OL,12,Fmany places as I could in the three
OL,13,Fminutes we had together."
OL,15,FSam Jones, prosecuting, asked: "Why
OL,16,Fdid you stab her so many times?"
OL,18,FThe defendant replied: "I didn't stab
OL,19,Fher so many times."
