OL,6,FMr Jones asked: "Why didn't you stop
OL,7,Fat any point?"
OL,9,FThe defendant said: "I did".
OL,11,FMr Jones replied: "You didn't, you
OL,12,Fkept going. You had to be stopped."
OL,14,FThe defendant told the court: "When
OL,15,Fthose men arrived and they were on my
OL,16,Fback, I was no longer doing anything
OL,17,Fto Emma."
