OL,6,FMr Jones said: "Even when the knife
OL,7,Fhad been prised out of your hands,
OL,8,Feven when you had all these people on
OL,9,Fyour back, trying to hold you down,
OL,10,Fyou were reaching out in one last
OL,11,Fattempt to strangle her as she bled on
OL,12,Fthe ground."
OL,14,FThe defendant replied: "No."
OL,16,FHe denied grabbing at Miss Kirk's neck
OL,17,Fand instead claimed he had been trying
OL,18,Fto push her clothing to her neck.
