OL,3,CMan denies trying to kill fellow
OL,4,Cteacher with knife after rejection
OL,6,FMr Jones, prosecuting, previously
OL,7,Fdescribed how Jones and Miss Kirk met
OL,8,Fat university before becoming
OL,9,F"romantically involved".
OL,11,FThe attack took place after Miss Kirk
OL,12,Ftold Jones she did not wish to see him
OL,13,Fagain but agreed to meet him in a lane
OL,14,Fnear her home to return Christmas
OL,15,Fgifts he had given her.
OL,17,FIt is alleged that Jones then produced
OL,18,Fa knife and demanded to see Miss
OL,19,FKirk's mobile phone, causing her to
OL,20,Frun away. He is said to have pulled
OL,21,Fher to the ground before stabbing her.
