OL,6,FMiss Kirk sustained two punctured
OL,7,Flungs, and multiple wounds to her
OL,8,Fhands as she grabbed at the blade.
OL,10,FAn off-duty police officer, members of
OL,11,Fthe public and paramedics went to
OL,12,Fassist Miss Kirk, and administered
OL,13,Ffirst aid.
OL,15,FMr Jones, prosecuting, previously told
OL,16,Fjurors that Miss Kirk would have died
OL,17,Fif they had not done so.
