OL,3,CMan denies trying to kill fellow
OL,4,Cteacher with knife after rejection
OL,6,FThe defendant later told police it was
OL,7,FMiss Kirk who brought the knife to the
OL,8,Fscene, and he took it from her during
OL,9,Fa struggle in which they both ended up
OL,10,Fon the floor.
OL,12,FJones, of Ivy Avenue, Southdown, Bath,
OL,13,Fdenies charges of attempted murder and
OL,14,Fhaving an article with a blade or
OL,15,Fpoint in a public place. But he admits
OL,16,Fcausing her grievous bodily harm with
OL,17,Fintent.
OL,19,FThe trial continues.
